Cost-effectiveness of Venous Thromboembolism Prophylaxis After Hospitalization 
in Patients With Inflammatory Bowel Disease.

Lee KE(1), Lim F(2), Colombel JF(3), Hur C(2), Faye AS(4).

Author information:
(1)Vagelos College of Physicians and Surgeons, Columbia University, New York, 
NY, USA.
(2)Department of Medicine, Division of Digestive and Liver Diseases, 
NewYork-Presbyterian/Columbia University Irving Medical Center, New York, NY, 
USA.
(3)Division of Gastroenterology, Icahn School of Medicine at Mount Sinai, New 
