Addition of ramucirumab or merestinib to standard first-line chemotherapy for 
locally advanced or metastatic biliary tract cancer: a randomised, double-blind, 
multicentre, phase 2 study.

Valle JW(1), Vogel A(2), Denlinger CS(3), He AR(4), Bai LY(5), Orlova R(5), Van 
