Provision and related factors of end-of-life care in elderly housing with care 
services in collaboration with home-visiting nurse agencies: a nationwide 
survey.

Fukui S(1)(2), Otsuki N(3), Ikezaki S(4), Fukahori H(5), Irie S(6).

Author information:
(1)Department of Home Care nursing, Graduate School of Health Care Sciences, 
